Class Patch

  • java.lang.Object
    • nsp.Patch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Patch
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents a single discrete patch of potential habitat. Mainly serves to hold state variables that are then transformed by different classes. The state variables have private access and are modified using getters and setters.
